text: Julius 'Jack' Wegner (21 July 1913 – 30 April 1982) was an Australian rules footballer who played with Fitzroy in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * * Category:1913 births Category:1982 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Fitzroy Football Club players Category:Northcote Football Club players
